   [$ (^L. Town.^) $] You are a little too delicate (^Emilia^) .
[$ (^Enter a Page.^) $]
   [$ (^Page.^) $] Sir (^Fopling Flutter^) , Madam, desires to know if 
You are to be seen.
   [$ (^L. Town.^) $] Here's the freshest Fool in Town, and one 
